{"prompt": "Generate a website for a e-commerce store. The website should be sophisticated and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elegance Emporium</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #0d47a1;\n            --secondary-blue: #1976d2;\n            --accent-blue: #90caf9;\n            --text-color: #263238;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #eeeeee;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-align: center;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(13, 71, 161, 0.8), rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500?text=Sophisticated+Style') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            min-height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .products {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        .products h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .product-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .product-item {\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-blue);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .product-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(13, 71, 161, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .product-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .product-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .product-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .product-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .product-info .price {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        .product-item .buy-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: calc(100% - 40px);\n            margin: 0 20px 20px 20px;\n            padding: 12px 0;\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .product-item .buy-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Elegance Emporium</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#products\">Shop</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Discover Timeless Sophistication</h2>\n            <p>Curated collections for the discerning individual. Experience luxury redefined.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"products\" class=\"products\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Products</h2>\n            <div class=\"product-grid\">\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250?text=Classic+Watch\" alt=\"Classic Watch\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Classic Timepiece</h3>\n                        <p>An exquisite watch crafted with precision and elegance.</p>\n                        <div class=\"price\">$599.00</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250?text=Leather+Handbag\" alt=\"Leather Handbag\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Artisan Handbag</h3>\n                        <p>Handcrafted from premium leather for a luxurious feel.</p>\n                        <div class=\"price\">$750.00</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250?text=Silk+Scarf\" alt=\"Silk Scarf\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Designer Silk Scarf</h3>\n                        <p>Adorn yourself with this vibrantly printed pure silk scarf.</p>\n                        <div class=\"price\">$150.00</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250?text=Silver+Jewelry\" alt=\"Silver Jewelry\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <h3>Sterling Silver Necklace</h3>\n                        <p>A minimalist and elegant necklace for everyday wear.</p>\n                        <div class=\"price\">$220.00</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"products\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Elegance Emporium</h2>\n            <p style=\"max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; color: #444;\">\n                At Elegance Emporium, we believe in the enduring power of quality and timeless design. We meticulously select each item to bring you a collection that embodies sophistication, craftsmanship, and a touch of luxury. Our mission is to provide an unparalleled shopping experience, offering pieces that are not just products, but expressions of personal style and refined taste.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Elegance Emporium. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Contact us: support@eleganceemporium.com</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}